STATE
v.
Kenneth Aaron McNEILL. No. 212P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 17, 2006. Joan Cunningham, Assistant Attorney General, Thomas H. Lock, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 24th day of April 2006 by Defendant for Notice of Appeal:

"Motion Dismissed ex mero motu by order of the Court in conference this the 17th day of August 2006."
